      </div>

  <div class="content">
    <h3>Overview</h3>

    <p>
      Anthropology              : 20th and 21st century Chinese economic, social and cultural changes and continuities. Topics include rural development, revolution and reform
policies, gender and households, family planning, minorities, urbanization, and human rights.          </p>

    <p class="catalog-terms">
      Terms:              This course is not scheduled for the 2014-2015 academic year.          </p>

